<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078772" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo et toto Orbe Celeberrimo
             <lb/>Johanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p>Responsionem ad <rs key="B_991170515018605501" type="letter">tuas litteras</rs> <choice><abbr>a.</abbr><expan>ante</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>diem</expan></choice> VI <choice><abbr>Kalend.</abbr><expan>Kalendas</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>April.</abbr><expan>Aprilias</expan></choice> <add>exaratas</add> us<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que in hanc diem distuli non tantum propter negotio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum medico-practicorum multitudinem, verum etiam
             <lb/>ut Tibi Vir Doctissime ultimam <choice><abbr>Illustr.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimorum</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimorum</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatorum</rs> deliberationem significarem in eo quod
             <lb/>respicit Tui ad Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>motionem.</p>
<p>Nobilissimi itaque <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs> Salarium primo promiss<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>etiamnum offerunt, videlicet 1500 florenos venetos,
             <lb/>quorum quilibet rationem habet sesquialteram ad
             <lb/>florenum germanicum sive hollandicum. Salarium
             <lb/>istud extraordinarium esse et nemini in <rs type="organisation">Patavino
                <lb/>Archilyceo</rs> ab hac <choice><abbr>Sereniss.</abbr><expan>Serenissima</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Potentiss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr><expan>Potentissima</expan></choice> <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Republica</rs> so<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lutum, in confesso est apud omnes et italos, et exte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ros, ac pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim notum est Clarissimo et Amicissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermano</rs>. Si <choice><abbr>Illustr.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs> salari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>exhibuissent aut promisissent Tibi 1500 Thalerorum
             <lb/>uncialium quadringentis Ludovicis aureis Gallicis
             <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalentium, etiamnum utique exhiberent, atque
             <lb/>annuatim solverent post solemnes vocationis litte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ras: sed nunquam ipsi tale promiserunt aut exhi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>buerunt stipendium. Ego (fateor) rogavi ut peteres 
             <lb/>uodcumque stipendium etiam magnum: Sa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078773" n="1v"/><lb break="no"/>larium a Te petitum, communicavi D. D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatoribus</rs>,
             <lb/>qui rebus serio pensitatis, Teque maximi facientes
             <lb/>tandem decreverunt Tibi offerre 1500 florenos
             <lb/>venetos totidem sesquiflorenis germanicis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quiva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lentes. Ego eorundem parui mandatis monendo tamen
             <lb/>Te per Thaleros unciales intelligere totidem ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genti uncias. Ipsi dixerunt; si per Thaleros unciales
             <lb/>(uti nos credimus) intelligit totidem sesquiflorenos
             <lb/>germanicos, seu totidem florenos nostros venetos,
             <lb/>Dominus Bernoullius, ipsum solemniter voca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bimus, sin autem intelligit totidem argenti un<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cias, actum est de ipsius promotione. Nos etenim
             <lb/>(sunt illorum verba) <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs> <rs type="organisation">Archilycei
             <lb/>Patavini</rs> <choice><sic>difficilim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></sic><corr>difficillim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></corr></choice><!-- l mit Schlinge = Doppel-l? --> obtinebimus a nostro
             <lb/><rs type="organisation">Senatu</rs> ut salarium 1500 florenorum veneto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum D. Bernoullio annuatim solvamus; qu<unclear>o</unclear><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>niam est insolitum neque <rs key="pers_DE-588-118537229" type="person">Galileo</rs>, neque <rs key="pers_DE-588-118784633" type="person">Mon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tanario</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmino</rs>, aut <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermano</rs> solutum. Plus
             <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimamus D. Bernoullium quam memoratos Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>thematicos, ideoque stipendium maius et insoli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum ipsi proponimus, atque persolvemus. Collige
             <lb/>ex his Vir <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice> si unquam D. D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs>
<lb/>Tibi proposuerunt salarium 1500 unciarum
             <pb facs="1078774" n="2r"/>
<lb/>argenti. Frustra igitur quereris dicendo Tibi salarium
             <lb/>prius oblatum postea fuisse diminutum. Maiestas <choice><abbr>Ill.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimorum</expan></choice>
<lb/>et <choice><abbr>Exell.<hi rend="sup"/></abbr><expan>Exellentissimorum</expan></choice><note type="internal">sic (ohne c)</note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatorum</rs> <rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mittet, dabit; et si promisisset 1500 ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genti uncias, profect<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> easdem persolveret. </p>
<p>Quod ad me pertinet Vir <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> omnem operam me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
         <lb/>collocavi, nihil intentatum reliqui ut Tibi inser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>virem, remque pro Te maximo cum amore per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tractavi. A D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermano</rs> animi mei candorem resci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re poteris. Exterus sum et quidem Tridentinus etsi
         <lb/>in hac inclita Civitate Medicinam practicam exer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ceam: quare exteros diligo, sed Vos pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ceteris Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>theseos, et quidem ipso <rs key="pers_DE-588-118503863" type="person">Archimede</rs> maiores, Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gistros. </p>
<p>Dolet <choice><abbr>Ampliss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Amplissimus</expan></choice> Moderator <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzinus</rs> quod Tu nequeas
             <lb/>votis suis satisfacere. Doleo ipse quod non potuerim
             <lb/>negotium istud ad mentem tuam dirigere. Hoc
             <lb/>tamen non impediet quominus tentem adhuc
             <lb/>(quoniam de tuo adventu nobis est desperandum)
             <lb/>num possim obtinere promotionem ad eandem
             <lb/><rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> Doctissimi Agnati Tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolai</rs>, cuius
             <lb/>in Mathematicis summam peritiam agnoscent etiam
             <lb/>inviti malevoli isti Itali postquam viderint eius<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dem <rs type="biblio">Annotationes</rs> in <rs key="biblio_QETMIRCN" type="biblio">schediasma</rs> Comitis <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccati</rs><choice><orig>;</orig><reg>,</reg></choice>
<lb/>quas quidem Annotationes revera ingeniosas, et
             <pb facs="1078775" n="2v"/>
<lb/>lectu dignas statim in linguam italicam verti, et
             <lb/>ut in publicum prodirent in Tomo XX Diarii Veneti
             <lb/>(quod sub pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lo est) curavi. Diarii Veneti Authores
             <lb/><choice><sic>dificillime</sic><corr>difficillime</corr></choice> annuebant meis votis, seseque excusabant
             <lb/>dicentes. Non possumus exterorum schediasmata
             <lb/>nostro Diario Litteratorum <rs key="place_KON-italie" type="place">Itali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> inserere: ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum ego omnes superavi difficultates. Curavi ut accu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rate prodir<choice><orig><g ref="#en">ē</g></orig><reg>en</reg></choice>t et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>caverentur vitia typographica
             <lb/>in analiticis expressionibus. Post quin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>decim circiter dies <rs key="biblio_QETMIRCN" type="biblio">schediasma Typis editum</rs> ad
             <lb/>vos mittam. Comes <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs> responsionem mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>natur, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> si prodibit, a me ad vos transmittetur
             <lb/>sine mora. Interim rogo ut quamprimum respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deas ad mea problemata in <rs key="B_991170515018705501" type="letter">antecedente mea epis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tola</rs> proposita.</p>
<p>Scripta calculi differentialis, et integralis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tuis di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scipulis<!-- Noch zu recherchieren? Könnte man versuchen, ist aber nicht unbedingt nötig --> communicasti<note type="internal">Bibliographieren</note> libenter etiam ego haberem
             <lb/>cum figuris, et quidem pulchre exarata: quare si
             <lb/>aliquis Discipulus apud Te esset qui Laborem non
             <lb/>recusaret, solverem duodecim aut quindecim ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genti uncias ut eadem scripta obtinerem, ea intelli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>go qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi ostendit <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerus</rs>.<note type="editorial">Scheuchzers Abschrift von Johanns Vorlesungen</note> Ego qui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dem in calculo differentiali et integrali (quorum utrumque
             <lb/>Tibi, et <choice><sic>Celeberimo</sic><corr>Celeberrimo</corr></choice> Fratri tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobo</rs> deberi fateor)
             <lb/>non minus versatus sum quam Comes <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs> qui
             <lb/>est mente valde superbus ingeniosus tamen, et valde
             <lb/>doctus: verum quemadmodum regulas calculi
             <pb facs="1078776" n="3r"/>
<lb/>differentialis et integralis vestras a D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermano</rs> (cui
             <lb/>multum debeo) accepi, it<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> libenter scripta Tuis
             <lb/>discipulis dictata in fasciculum collecta, et rite
             <lb/>exarata cum figuris necessariis acciperem. Si i<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gitur aliquis discipulus laborem non timebit, Tuque
             <lb/>mihi favere voles, persolvam discipulo scribenti
             <lb/>duodecim aut quindecim argenti uncias ut scripta
             <lb/>tua accipiam; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in fasciculum collecta per
